  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of an adorable dungeon keeper in <strong>One Room Dungeon</strong>, where roguelike team-building meets strategic inventory management. Your tiny one-room dungeon is your fortress—masterfully arrange your minions, whimsical relics, and delightful items to fend off pesky adventurers looking to raid your home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=320 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grid-Based Inventory Management</strong><br>Organize your dungeon with care using a grid-based system. Every item has its place, and your success depends on clever planning and tidy arrangements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=640 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Up Units and Items</strong><br>Strengthen your minions and magical artifacts over time. A well-trained team and upgraded gear are key to surviving tougher waves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultimate Skills</strong><br>Each unit has a unique Ultimate skill that activates when certain conditions are met—turning the tide of battle in a flash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=500 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Encounters</strong><br>Meet quirky friends and shopkeepers who may offer you rare items, game-changing gear, or curious relics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/e7c85ada675b5f24108fe34b4f35705d.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/e7c85ada675b5f24108fe34b4f35705d.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/e7c85ada675b5f24108fe34b4f35705d.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relics, Equipment, and Potions</strong><br>Find and combine different enhancements to build powerful synergies and create new tactics in every run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Bosses</strong><br>Put your strategy and strength to the test against mighty bosses that require more than just brute force to defeat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Starter Characters and Builds</strong><br>Choose from a range of starter characters, each with their own playstyle and skills. Pair them with starter relics to shape your run in entirely different ways.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your dungeon (your home), <strong>defeat the adventurers</strong>, and prove yourself as the ultimate dungeon keeper in <strong>One Room Dungeon</strong>!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of an adorable dungeon keeper in <strong>One Room Dungeon</strong>, where roguelike team-building meets strategic inventory management. Your tiny one-room dungeon is your fortress—masterfully arrange your minions, whimsical relics, and delightful items to fend off pesky adventurers looking to raid your home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=320 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grid-Based Inventory Management</strong><br>Organize your dungeon with care using a grid-based system. Every item has its place, and your success depends on clever planning and tidy arrangements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=640 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Up Units and Items</strong><br>Strengthen your minions and magical artifacts over time. A well-trained team and upgraded gear are key to surviving tougher waves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultimate Skills</strong><br>Each unit has a unique Ultimate skill that activates when certain conditions are met—turning the tide of battle in a flash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=500 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Encounters</strong><br>Meet quirky friends and shopkeepers who may offer you rare items, game-changing gear, or curious relics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/e7c85ada675b5f24108fe34b4f35705d.poster.avif?t=1772419810\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/e7c85ada675b5f24108fe34b4f35705d.webm?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/e7c85ada675b5f24108fe34b4f35705d.mp4?t=1772419810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relics, Equipment, and Potions</strong><br>Find and combine different enhancements to build powerful synergies and create new tactics in every run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Bosses</strong><br>Put your strategy and strength to the test against mighty bosses that require more than just brute force to defeat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Starter Characters and Builds</strong><br>Choose from a range of starter characters, each with their own playstyle and skills. Pair them with starter relics to shape your run in entirely different ways.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your dungeon (your home), <strong>defeat the adventurers</strong>, and prove yourself as the ultimate dungeon keeper in <strong>One Room Dungeon</strong>!</p>",
